Interface Tree<K,D>

Type Parameters:
K - type of the key value
D - type of the data object
All Known Implementing Classes:
AVLDictionary, AVLTree, BinarySearchTree, BinaryTree
public interface Tree<K,D>
Interface for a generic Tree data structure
